eir students.\"\n\nIllegal alien rapes and murders someone... \"Most immigrants are law abiding.\"\n\nDrunk driver kills family... \"Most drunk drivers don't actually crash.\"", "author": "XxxRDTPRNxxX", "created": 1776665282160, "profile_picture": "GzsU4lS5bp3X", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "eclectic22", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "New Logical Fallacy: Majoratism", "last_comment_created": 1776666715246, "content": "<p>Argument from majoratism: When something that happens frequently enough to be a valid concern is dismissed on the basis of it not happening the majority of the time.</p>\n<p>Examples: Muslim blows up a Christmas parade for the 5th time this year... &quot;Most Muslims are peaceful.&quot;</p>\n<p>Teacher grooms student to become a tranny and turn against their parents... &quot;Most teachers don't trans their students.&quot;</p>\n<p>Illegal alien rapes and murders someone... &quot;Most immigrants are law abiding.&quot;</p>\n<p>Drunk driver kills family... &quot;Most drunk drivers don't actually crash.&quot;</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 15, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZR8hHQV", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 62, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8568717, "raw_content": "", "author": "Tailgunnerjoe", "created": 1776637362990, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "